    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A private investigator, tracking a missing person, uncovers a conspiracy between humans and androids and a secret that could change everything. Neon Hearts City is a retro point-and-click adventure that thrusts you into a grungy cyberpunk city of the future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316640/extras/5591adcaa399ac480c7135ac1c5681d4.avif?t=1766864635\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316640/extras_big/5591adcaa399ac480c7135ac1c5681d4.avif?t=1766864635 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While searching for Audrey, a missing young girl, Elijah Crow's investigation takes a violent turn when one of his leads is silenced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Somewhere along the shore, androids longing to become human are offered as sacrifices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Far out at sea, a mysterious tower harbors secrets that could unravel the fabric of civilization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316640/extras/327ad2140b1ad8bb819674c8a02f284a.avif?t=1766864635\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316640/extras_big/327ad2140b1ad8bb819674c8a02f284a.avif?t=1766864635 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suspended in the sky, Roark Prison looms—a colossal airship where thought criminals face imprisonment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Somehow, these threads are inextricably intertwined.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316640/extras/072b62a797a83e880df78a8a9378a9fd.avif?t=1766864635\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316640/extras_big/072b62a797a83e880df78a8a9378a9fd.avif?t=1766864635 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game features</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Immersive cyberpunk pixel art.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Fully voiced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Play as a private detective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Explore the dystopian city of the future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Aid hunted-down androids.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Point and click puzzles &amp; item inventory.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Steam achievements!</p>",
